import React from "react";

export default function Meme(){
    return (
        <main>
            <form className="form">
                <input 
                     type="text"
                     placeholder="Top text"
                     className="form-input" />

                <input 
                type="text" 
                placeholder="Buttom text"
                className="form-input"/>
            

                <button className="form button"
                    onClick={getMemeImage}>Get a new Meme Image</button>

            </form>
        </main> 
    )
}
